---
import PublicLayout from '../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout title="Learning - Induction - EduX">
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] glow-blob -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none" style="--blob-color:rgba(168,85,247,0.1)"></div>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-12">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-amber-600/10 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/20 mb-6">
          Coming Soon
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">Learning — Induction</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Digital induction modules for new students. Cover learner rights, responsibilities, academic integrity, support services, and study skills — all tracked and reportable for compliance.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-xl text-base font-bold text-white bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 transition-all no-underline text-center">Register Interest</a>
          <a href="/register" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-xl text-base font-bold border border-slate-300 dark:border-white/20 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition-all no-underline text-center">Register RTO</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Planned Features -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-8">Planned Features</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="glass-panel rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 bg-purple-600/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Interactive Modules</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Engaging digital induction content that students complete online before or during their first week of enrolment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-panel rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 bg-purple-600/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Completion Tracking</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Track which students have completed their induction. Generate reports for compliance evidence and follow up with incomplete students.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-panel rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 bg-purple-600/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Customisable Content</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Customise induction content to match your RTO's specific policies, procedures, and support services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-panel rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 bg-purple-600/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Rights & Responsibilities</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Cover learner rights and responsibilities, complaint and appeal processes, and academic integrity requirements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-panel rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 bg-purple-600/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Support Services</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Introduce students to available support services including LLN support, counselling, and disability services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-panel rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 bg-purple-600/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Compliance Evidence</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Generate audit-ready evidence that students have been properly inducted with timestamps and acknowledgements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-16">
      <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Be the first to know</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-lg mx-auto mb-8">The Learning — Induction portal is currently in development. Register your interest and we'll notify you at launch.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-xl text-base font-bold text-white bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 transition-all no-underline">Register Interest</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</PublicLayout>
